					<img src="https://assets.realclear.com/images/50/507327_5_.jpg" alt="It&rsquo;s Time for the White House to Focus on Drug Approvals" />
				<![endif]--></picture> <div class="hero_credit"><a class="attribution_url" target="_blank" href="https://realclearpolitics.com"> (AP Photo/Andrew Harnik)</a></div></div><div class="article-body-text"><div class="story-stream-hover-wrapper">
			<div class="story-stream-hover">
				<div class="mobile-close-btn">X</div>
				<div class="story-stream-hover-tab-up"></div>
